# Bill of Materials (BOM)

## 🧠 Controller & Electronics
| Item                     | Quantity | Description |
|--------------------------|----------|-------------|
| ESP32 Dev Board          | 1        | Main microcontroller with Wi-Fi/Bluetooth |
| PCA9685 Servo Driver     | 1        | 16-channel PWM driver for servos |
| BH1750 Light Sensor      | 1        | Ambient light sensor (I2C) |
| Jumper Wires             | 20+      | Male-to-male / female connections |
| Breadboard / PCB         | 1        | Prototyping connections |

## ⚙️ Actuators
| Item                     | Quantity | Description |
|--------------------------|----------|-------------|
| Servo Motors (MG90S/MG996R) | 8–12  | For leg movement |
| High Torque Servo (optional) | 1–2  | For future upgrades (tail/extra load) |

## 🔋 Power System
| Item                     | Quantity | Description |
|--------------------------|----------|-------------|
| Li-ion Battery (7.4V)    | 1        | Power source |
| Voltage Regulator (5V)   | 1        | Stable supply for servos |
| Power Switch             | 1        | On/Off control |
| Charging Module          | 1        | Battery charging (TP4056 or similar) |

## 🦾 Mechanical Parts
| Item                     | Quantity | Description |
|--------------------------|----------|-------------|
| 3D Printed Body Frame    | 1        | Main robot chassis |
| 3D Printed Legs          | 4        | Quadruped legs |
| Screws & Nuts (M2/M3)    | Set      | Assembly hardware |
| Bearings (optional)      | 4–8      | Smooth joint movement |

## 🧪 Development & Tools
| Item                     | Quantity | Description |
|--------------------------|----------|-------------|
| USB Cable (Type-C/Micro) | 1        | Programming ESP32 |
| Laptop / PC              | 1        | Development environment |
| Wokwi Simulator          | -        | Virtual testing |

